  "title": "Junior Service Crew (High-End Restuarant) – Immediate Hiring",
  "description": "<p>📍 Location: Tanjong Pagar</p><p>💰 Salary: $2,500 – $2,700<br /></p><p>Job Responsibilities:</p><p>- Prepare and set up the outlet for food service</p><p>- Greet guests and introduce the menu; recommend dishes and drinks</p><p>- Attend to guests’ needs and handle queries or concerns</p><p>- Take and serve food & beverage orders accurately</p><p>- Present checks and collect bill payments</p><p>- Maintain basic knowledge of menu items, specials, and promotions</p><p>- Assist with deliveries and stock management as needed</p><p>- Keep the restaurant and equipment clean and organized</p><p>- Perform ad-hoc duties as assigned<br /></p><p>Benefits:</p><p>- 5-day work week, 44 hours per week</p><p>- Quarterly sales incentives program</p><p>- Loyalty bonus: after 1 year – $100/month; after 3 years – $300/month<br /></p><p>Requirements:</p><p>- Friendly, approachable, and team-oriented</p><p>- Able to work flexible shifts, including weekends and public holidays</p><p>- Prior F&B or customer service experience preferred but not mandatory<br /></p><p>✨ Grow your F&B career with a supportive team and rewarding incentives!<br /></p><p>How to Apply:</p><p>📞 WhatsApp: wa.me/6589387313<br /></p><p>Send with Code: <strong>JUNIORCREW</strong> + these details:</p><p>✅ Full Name</p><p>✅ Residential Area</p><p>✅ Earliest Availability Date</p><p>✅ Commitment Period</p><p>✅ Able to work on weekends? (Y/N)</p><p>✅ Attach Resume</p><p>And please attached a copy of your resume</p><p>https://t.me/sgbesttempjobs</p><p>https://t.me/varioustempjobs<br /></p><p>Chia Xin Ee Crystal | R21103390</p><p>EA License No: 21C0626</p>",
